OL,5,G2000 Location, Location, Location
OL,6,     FWe're back in London. Have
OL,7,     Fmusicians Molly and Sam found
OL,8,     Fharmony and a home? And it's a
OL,9,     FCrystal Palace catch up with Alan
OL,10,     Fand Rachel, who've really made
OL,11,     Ftheir home their own.
OL,12,G2100 24 Hours in A&E
OL,13,     FIn Nottingham, David's collapsed
OL,14,     Fat home with a suspected stroke.
OL,15,     FCecil's in A&E after his motorbike
OL,16,     Fcrashed at 130mph. And Tanya's had
OL,17,     Fa possible seizure on a night out.
